    /// # Input
    /// ## min
    /// The smallest integer to be drawn.
    /// ## max
    /// The largest integer to be drawn.
    ///
    /// # Output
    /// An integer in the inclusive range from `min` to `max` with uniform
    /// probability.
    ///
    /// # Remarks
    /// Fails if `max <= min`.
